31:13.163 --> 31:15.916
Let’s talk about me.

31:16.000 --> 31:17.293
I’m an alcoholic.

31:18.544 --> 31:20.421
I lost my hearing
in the Vietnam War

31:20.504 --> 31:23.674
when a bomb exploded near me.

31:23.757 --> 31:25.759
I still remember the music
I was listening to

31:25.843 --> 31:26.969
when that bomb went off.

31:28.512 --> 31:32.558
After that,
I lost everything else--

31:32.641 --> 31:35.769
my wife, my kid.

31:35.853 --> 31:37.980
Not because of being deaf,
mind you, Ruben.

31:38.063 --> 31:39.356
It was the beer.

31:42.443 --> 31:44.570
How long you been clean?

31:45.904 --> 31:47.323
Four years.

31:47.406 --> 31:49.825
-Four?
-Mmm.

31:49.908 --> 31:52.494
And you need some help
right now?

31:53.746 --> 31:55.706
Yo, I should check on Lou.

31:57.666 --> 31:59.251
How long you two been together?

32:00.628 --> 32:02.963
Four years.

32:03.047 --> 32:06.342
-

32:25.736 --> 32:27.905
You play music, right?

32:27.988 --> 32:29.323
-No.
-No?

32:29.406 --> 32:30.532
No, not anymore.

32:30.616 --> 32:32.284
Not until I get the implant.

32:32.368 --> 32:34.536
-Implant?
-Yeah.

32:34.620 --> 32:37.039
Sorry, you know about
these implants they got now?

32:37.122 --> 32:39.375
It’s like... it’s like, uh...
th-they have implants.

32:39.458 --> 32:42.419
I know. Yes.

32:42.503 --> 32:43.504
Expensive.

32:43.587 --> 32:46.757
Yeah. Thank you.
Yes, they are.

32:46.840 --> 32:48.258
So...

32:50.094 --> 32:52.012
You should understand that, uh,

32:52.096 --> 32:53.389
this is a Deaf community.

32:53.472 --> 32:55.849
Not just my program,
but we’re part

32:55.933 --> 32:57.935
of a larger Deaf community.

32:58.018 --> 33:01.814
And my program,
and the people in it,

33:01.897 --> 33:05.275
they benefit tremendously
from that Deaf community.

33:05.359 --> 33:06.944
We work with them,

33:07.027 --> 33:08.445
and they work with us.

33:08.529 --> 33:11.448
But it’s very important,

33:11.532 --> 33:12.950
if you want to be here,

33:13.033 --> 33:14.451
to understand
that we’re looking for

33:14.535 --> 33:16.245
a solution to...

33:16.328 --> 33:18.122
to this...

33:19.081 --> 33:20.290
...not this.

33:23.585 --> 33:26.130
Why don’t you go
invite Lou in here?

33:29.341 --> 33:31.427
Sure.

33:34.263 --> 33:35.806
Lou!

33:42.896 --> 33:44.857
This guy wants to talk to you.

33:44.940 --> 33:46.775
Okay.

33:50.320 --> 33:52.114
Well... I think it’s important

33:52.197 --> 33:54.658
that you stay here
with us right now, Ruben,

33:54.742 --> 33:56.410
learn some sign language,

33:56.493 --> 33:58.412
find some solid ground.

33:59.580 --> 34:00.956
What do you think?

34:01.039 --> 34:02.458
Man, it sounds great,

34:02.541 --> 34:04.209
but we don’t have
a lot of money right now.

34:04.293 --> 34:06.879
