sponsors deaf people in need,

34:06.962 --> 34:08.714
and right now,

34:08.797 --> 34:10.507
you fit the bill, Ruben.

34:10.591 --> 34:11.925
Uh, we’re really not

34:12.009 --> 34:13.510
-churchgoing people.
-Sorry, I-I read...

34:13.594 --> 34:15.095
Sorry, Ruben, I read lips.
I can’t...

34:15.179 --> 34:16.472
What’d you say?

34:17.556 --> 34:19.975
We’re not religious,
either of us.

34:20.058 --> 34:21.393
Very much not into religion.

34:21.477 --> 34:22.811
No offense, you know.

34:22.895 --> 34:25.105
Religion plays no part
in this, Ruben.

34:25.189 --> 34:26.648
The church helps

34:26.732 --> 34:28.692
people in need,
not religious people.

34:28.776 --> 34:31.069
The important thing is that
you want to stay here.

34:31.153 --> 34:32.529
Mmm.

34:32.613 --> 34:33.655
Yeah.

34:33.739 --> 34:34.907
Lou?

34:34.990 --> 34:37.493
