to that, Lou?

35:06.230 --> 35:07.689
You want... you want to
try this for a couple days?

35:07.773 --> 35:08.607
We have our own home.

35:08.690 --> 35:10.526
We can stay in the RV.

35:10.609 --> 35:12.236
No, I’m sorry to say,
that’s not the way

35:12.319 --> 35:13.153
that it works here, Ruben.

35:13.237 --> 35:15.197
Well, that’s a problem, then.

35:15.280 --> 35:18.033
Do you have anywhere you can be
during this time, Lou?

35:19.910 --> 35:22.538
Yo, that’s that, man.
We’re done.

35:22.621 --> 35:23.580
We’re done.

35:23.664 --> 35:24.706
Thanks a lot for your time, bro.

35:24.790 --> 35:25.874
Appreciate it, okay?

35:25.958 --> 35:27.334
We’re out, baby. Let’s go.

35:56.655 --> 35:57.865
Hey.

36:00.158 --> 36:01.660
