we should still go hit

36:01.743 --> 36:03.161
our fuckin’ show in Dayton.

36:03.245 --> 36:05.372
Okay? I can... I can
fuckin’ watch you for cues.

36:05.455 --> 36:07.499
I know it was rocky last time,
but we did...

36:07.583 --> 36:08.959
