36:09.042 --> 36:10.961
Now you know what’s up,
I can fuckin’ watch you.

36:11.044 --> 36:13.005
And I know this shit inside out.

36:13.088 --> 36:14.631
Okay, yo.
I can fuckin’ make it work

36:14.715 --> 36:17.968
until we have enough
for surgery.

36:18.051 --> 36:18.886
Okay?

36:18.969 --> 36:21.013
We’re gonna get there.

36:21.096 --> 36:23.432
Yo, seriously, we’re good to go.

36:23.515 --> 36:24.975
Lou.

36:25.058 --> 36:27.060
Hmm?

36:27.144 --> 36:29.062
Hey, I’ll deal with this shit.

36:29.146 --> 36:30.147
I’ll deal with it.

36:30.230 --> 36:31.940
You know I fucking will.
It’s just money.

36:32.024 --> 36:33.859
