to that place.

39:12.434 --> 39:14.186
Just slow down, okay?
Slow down.

39:14.269 --> 39:16.021
Yo, chill, dude.
We’re gonna be a minute.

39:16.104 --> 39:18.440
Just chill. Okay?

39:18.523 --> 39:20.525
Just slow down a minute.

39:20.609 --> 39:22.319
Lou. Lou.

39:22.402 --> 39:23.779
This is so fucked up.

39:23.862 --> 39:25.697
Who’s gonna be looking out
for you over there? Hmm?

39:25.781 --> 39:27.324
-Who’s gonna look out for you?
-It’s okay.

39:27.407 --> 39:28.825
-Don’t say that guy.
-It’s okay. It’s okay.

39:28.909 --> 39:30.744
Lou, I need...
I need more of a plan, Lou.

39:30.827 --> 39:31.870
-Ruben.
-I need...

39:31.953 --> 39:33.914
I need more from you, Lou.

39:41.838 --> 39:44.216
I need more of a plan, Lou.

39:44.299 --> 39:46.218
You can’t just fuckin’...

39:56.228 --> 39:58.522
Ah, Jesus. Lou, come on.

39:58.605 --> 40:00.774
Ruben. Ruben.

40:01.817 --> 40:03.318
You hurt yourself...

40:03.401 --> 40:05.612
Ruben, you hurt yourself,

40:05.695 --> 40:06.988
you hurt me.

40:07.072 --> 40:09.699
I’ll hurt myself, too.
I’ll hurt myself, too.

40:09.783 --> 40:11.743
Don’t say that.

40:11.827 --> 40:13.203
Promise.

40:13.286 --> 40:15.497
Say it, Rubi,
or all of this is for shit.

40:15.580 --> 40:16.623
Say it! Promise!

40:16.706 --> 40:17.999
Go back there right now.

40:18.083 --> 40:19.417
Promise, say it!

40:19.501 --> 40:22.379
-I’ll promise if you...
-No, say it, promise.

40:26.049 --> 40:27.259
Go back to that place.

40:27.342 --> 40:29.594
I... only if... I need...

40:29.678 --> 40:31.721
I need you to wait for me.

40:31.805 --> 40:34.099
Okay? You’re it for me, Lou.
You’re my fuckin’ heart.

40:34.182 --> 40:35.517
You’re it for me.

40:35.600 --> 40:38.270
Okay? You got to wait for me.

40:46.153 --> 40:47.612
Fuck.

40:50.574 --> 40:51.867
Listen to me. Listen, listen.

40:51.950 --> 40:54.953
When you get there,
I need you to...

40:55.036 --> 40:57.247
I need you to write to me, okay?

40:57.330 --> 41:00.792
Yeah? Will you write me
and tell me you’re okay?

41:00.876 --> 41:02.169
Huh? Promise me?

41:02.252 --> 41:03.587
And listen, if it’s...

41:03.670 --> 41:05.755
if it’s bullshit,
you just get your ass back here.

41:05.839 --> 41:07.257
I’ll fix it, I swear to God.

41:07.340 --> 41:08.508
You know I’ll fuckin’ fix this.

41:08.592 --> 41:10.343
This is not that hard, okay?

41:10.427 --> 41:12.304
Just come back here.

41:15.640 --> 41:17.475
-I love you.
-You’re my fucking heart.

41:17.559 --> 41:18.810
Okay?

41:21.229 --> 41:22.731
Motherfucker.

41:22.814 --> 41:24.900
-Oh, motherf...
-

41:33.241 --> 41:35.452
-Fuck.
-

