54:40.528 --> 54:41.946
It’s, like,
one of the eaves is...

54:42.029 --> 54:44.115
:
I was trying to fix your roof.

54:44.198 --> 54:47.118
You don’t need to fix
anything here.

54:58.754 --> 55:00.214
I’ve got a little, uh...

55:00.297 --> 55:02.466
