55:02.550 --> 55:05.803
You get up early, right?

55:05.886 --> 55:07.680
Yeah, pretty early, yeah.

55:09.181 --> 55:10.850
I’ll have hot coffee

55:10.933 --> 55:12.351
waiting for you

55:12.435 --> 55:14.186
