55:14.270 --> 55:16.522
Early enough for you?

55:19.859 --> 55:21.485
I don’t know. I guess.

55:21.569 --> 55:23.654
Okay, 5:00.

55:23.738 --> 55:25.656
And I’ll, uh,

55:25.740 --> 55:27.742
provide a room for you.

55:27.825 --> 55:29.577
What for?

55:29.660 --> 55:32.580
