56:02.693 --> 56:04.403
...mess.

56:04.487 --> 56:06.280
I don’t care.

56:06.363 --> 56:08.908
No one will read it, okay?

56:08.991 --> 56:10.993
But I want you to keep writing

56:11.077 --> 56:12.912
continuously without stopping

56:12.995 --> 56:15.790
until you feel like you can...

56:18.000 --> 56:20.086
...sit again.

56:35.351 --> 56:37.520
