-Writing, yes.

56:37.603 --> 56:40.397
No drawing. Writing, yes.

56:45.111 --> 56:47.613
And if...
sometime in the future,

56:47.696 --> 56:50.908
it feels like it’s a little bit
too difficult for you,

56:50.991 --> 56:53.953
